 98 West George St Glasgow G2 1PJ<br /><br />Or go to <a href="http://www.paih.org/donate" rel="nofollow">http://www.paih.org/donate</a><br /><br />An appeal by Positive Action in Housing (Registered charity SC027577)<br /><br />‪Please donate to our Winter Destitution Appeal, helping child refugees, individuals and families fleeing war who are now left at risk of destitution and hunger.<br /><br />Many of the people who have arrived here took dangerous journeys across the Mediterranean to reach safety. <br /><br />Now that war refugees are here and we need to help them. <br /><br /><a href="https://mydonate.bt.com/events/winterrefugeecrisisappeal/371911" rel="nofollow">https://mydonate.bt.com/events/winterrefugeecrisisappeal/371911</a><br /><br />Our winter surgery this week will assist 300-400 refugee children and families from Syria, Iraq, Afghanistan, Eritrea and elsewhere . <br /><br />Destitution grants are being distributed in Glasgow, Edinburgh and London.<br /><br />Please donate now and help us make a difference <br /><br /><a href="https://mydonate.bt.com/events/winterrefugeecrisisappeal/371911" rel="nofollow">https://mydonate.bt.com/events/winterrefugeecrisisappeal/371911</a><br /><br />Positive Action in Housing <br />Working together to rebuild lives</p>        <div class="fb_link_post">          <a href="http://www.glasgowlive.co.uk/news/glasgow-news/give-up-spare-room-make-12339277"><img src="http://i4.glasgowlive.co.uk/incoming/article11828137.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200/JS98397454.jpg" alt="Facebook Picture" width="130" height="130" />          </a>          <h6><a href="http://www.glasgowlive.co.uk/news/glasgow-news/give-up-spare-room-make-12339277">Give up a spare room or make a donation to help refugees in Glasgow this winter</a></h6>          <p class="fb_cap"><a href="http://www.glasgowlive.co.uk" rel="nofollow">http://www.glasgowlive.co.uk</a></p>          <p class="fb_desc">Glasgow refugee and migrant homelessness charity need help supporting refugees who otherwise would be without housing or basics this winter</p>        </div>      </div>      <div class="fb_commLink">        <span class="fb_comment">          <a href="http://www.glasgowlive.co.uk/news/glasgow-news/give-up-spare-room-make-12339277">Comment</a>        </span>        <span>          <a title="20 people like this" href="http://www.glasgowlive.co.uk/news/glasgow-news/give-up-spare-room-make-12339277"><span class="fb_likes_count">20</span><span class="fb_likes"></span></a>        </span>      </div>      <div style="clear: both;"></div>    </div>    <div class="fb_post">      <div class="fb_photoblock">        <div class="fb_photo">          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/PositiveActionH/">            <img src="https://graph.facebook.com/305725750313/picture?type=normal" alt="Facebook Profile Pic" />          </a>        </div>        <div class="fb_photo_content">          <h5>            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/PositiveActionH/">Positive Action in Housing</a>          </h5>          <div class="fb_time">            <img class="fb_post_icon" src="https://www.facebook.com/images/icons/photo.gif" alt="Facebook Icon" />17th December 2016 at 21:47          </div>        </div>      </div>      <div class="fb_msg">        <p>LONDON HOME URGENTLY NEEDED TO HOST SYRIAN FAMILY RECENTLY ARRIVED FROM ALEPPO <br /><br />We are trying to assist a professional , educated Syrian couple and their two year old baby daughter. They are from Aleppo. Khalid and his wife. If you can provide free shelter in your home or in separate accommodation to this family for 3 months or longer please email <a href="mailto:Robina@positiveactionh.org">Robina@positiveactionh.org</a> . Your support will mean they can start to seek work in their chosen professions of architecture and banking and eventually resettle independently on their own. <br /><br />IF YOU CAN HELP PLEASE REGISTER AT <a href="http://WWW.ROOMFORREFUGEES.COM" rel="nofollow">http://WWW.ROOMFORREFUGEE