div>      <div class="fb_msg">        <p>Beautiful message of thanks to Room for Refugees from the members of  Sharedydd in Cardiff, Wales <br /><br />&quot;Thank you for the amazing and dedicated support you offer to the community here in Cardiff. Without your Room for Refugees programme and the careful support it provides we&rsquo;d be a lot more limited in what we can do. In 2016 Sharedydd has supported tens and tens of people...sometimes for just 1 night, a more than a few for many months. Other people we just provide reassurance that we are here as a last resort. Once again we&rsquo;ll have provided more than 1000 nights of accommodation in 2016. It&#039;s not possible to do this without our generous and kind hosts and donors.&quot;<br /><br />Many thanks,<br /><br />Andy, Bex, David, Francis, Jacci, Jacky, Patrick and Pete.<br /><br />Sharedydd</p>        <div class="fb_link_post">          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/PositiveActionH/photos/a.10150154323190314.398019.305725750313/10158108869170314/?type=3"><img src="https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/s130x130/15589759_10158108869170314_7516600600593717841_n.jpg?oh=f75ad70357899e6a19284d9f7d43d28c&amp;oe=58E3ECB2" alt="Facebook Picture" />          </a>          <h6><a href="https://www.facebook.com/PositiveActionH/photos/a.10150154323190314.398019.305725750313/10158108869170314/?type=3">Timeline Photos</a></h6>        </div>      </div>      <div class="fb_commLink">        <span class="fb_comment">          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/PositiveActionH/photos/a.10150154323190314.398019.305725750313/10158108869170314/?type=3">Comment</a>        </span>        <span>          <a title="1 people like this" href="https://www.facebook.com/PositiveActionH/photos/a.10150154323190314.398019.305725750313/10158108869170314/?type=3"><span class="fb_likes_count">1</span><span class="fb_likes"></span></a>        </span>      </div>      <div style="clear: both;"></div>    </div>    <div class="fb_post">     